dct_title_s: Taal and Lemery, Philippine Islands, Batangas Province. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: Taal and Lemery. In upper left margin: Philippine Islands city plans. Depth shown by soundings in feet at mean lower low water. "From survey in 1905." Copied from U.S.C.&G.S. chart 4257.
